Join us for an exclusive conversation with the talented Kritika Kamra on iDiva x Veet India Talking Stage! 🌟 In this episode, Kritika shares insights into her incredible acting journey, spills the beans on her favorite glam hack that she just can't get enough of, and reveals her ultimate midnight snack indulgence. 💄🍕

But that's not all! Dive deep into Kritika's wisdom on relationships as she unveils her top relationship hack to gracefully move on from a past connection. 🌹🔐 Explore the nuances of female friendship in the digital age and gain valuable perspectives on handling internet trolls while maintaining mental well-being. 🤝💻

And the excitement doesn't end there! Get an exclusive sneak peek into Kritika's upcoming series, Gyarah Gyarah and For Your Eyes Only. 🎬✨ Don't miss out on this engaging and insightful conversation that decodes the Gen Z lexicon with one of the most talented actors in the industry. Hit play now and stay tuned for a rollercoaster of emotions, laughter, and wisdom! 🎙️📺

#TalkingStage #KritikaKamra #CelebrityInterview #idiva #celebritygossip

latestPosts.caption:
In a world where strength and resilience are often portrayed through a filtered lens, Mandira Bedi stands tall as a beacon of courage and unwavering determination. From establishing herself in the entertainment industry as an actress and a TV presenter to breaking stereotypes in the fitness world, she has inspired many and continues to do so.

Despite facing personal and professional challenges, her unbreakable spirit has always led her to rise above adversity. A true symbol of perseverance, Mandira has always proved that women can excel in anything they set their hearts and minds to. Her journey is a powerful reminder that real confidence comes from facing challenges head-on! 🌸
Here’s introducing #IconsOfNewhood, a series featuring women who don’t just follow trends, but set them with a unique style and perspective that others are eager to emulate. Stay tuned for more! ✨
